org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT statuses.id AS alias_0, accounts.id FROM accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN statuses ON statuses.deleted_at IS NULL AND statuses.account_id = accounts.id LEFT OUTER JOIN account_stats ON account_stats.account_id = accounts.id WHERE accounts.suspended_at IS NULL AND statuses.deleted_at IS NULL AND statuses.reblog_of_id = "$1" AND statuses.visibility IN ("$2", "$3") ORDER BY statuses.id DESC LIMIT "$4"
